divs: sighting detailswalk outside to have a smoke on deck. moon had not come up yet so it was very dark and good time to watch the stars. noticed a what can only be described as a star way moving nw to se in the sky. no blinking lights..figured hey i get to see a satellite but this thing was moving very very fast. well across 3\4 of my view of skyline above the trees this object changed course and headed ne. i'm talking turn on a dime. after this nothing else happened. only wish i had my camera. never seen anything like this in my life.
Summary: Moving star high in the sky
